msgid ""
"data/text_blueprints.xml.append$//text[@name=\"text_PLAYER_SHIP_TRASH_MINER_desc\"]"
msgstr ""
"An old Kestrel class ship intended for light asteroid mining and garbage "
"removal. Refitted for combat by the Sergal Engineer Cheese, who was joined "
"by the Protogen TRACKER and Primagen RAPTOR. A malfunction in the clonebay's"
" DNA Backup created Lancer."

